 eisenberg to establish the republican leadership council in  he also contributed one million dollars to donald j trumps presidential inauguration  philanthropy and public positionsedit the henry r kravis prize in nonprofit leadership established in  identifies extraordinary leaders in the nonprofit sector celebrates their accomplishments and shares their best practices with others the prize is presented and administered by claremont mckenna college cmc and mariejosée and henry kravis kravis is an alumnus and trustee of claremont mckenna college the kravis prize is affiliated with the kravis leadership institute a research institute at claremont mckenna a formal award ceremony celebrates the recipients accomplishments and  is directed to a nonprofit organization designated by the recipient kravis also funds the henry kravis leadership institute that sponsors the leadership studies programs at claremont mckenna college and the henry kravis internships for teachers of color program he has also financed the construction of extensive facilities at middlesex school kravis house the eaglebrook school kravis dorm deerfield academy kravis arena and the loomis chaffee school kravis hall he is a benefactor and a past chairman of new yorks public television station and sits on the board of the metropolitan museum of art a trustee of the mount sinai medical center henry and wife mariejosée kravis donated  million to establish the center for cardiovascular health as well as funding a professorship they have also endowed the chair in human oncology at memorial sloankettering cancer center in new york he previously cochaired with jerry speyer the influential partnership for new york city founded by david rockefeller in  and now sits on its board of directors he created the new york city investment fund a nonprofit organization to create jobs and new business in new york city he is a trustee of the council on foreign relations in new york chairman of sponsors for educational opportunity and is a member of the executive committee of the business council for    and  he cochairs the columbia business school board of overseers where he recently pledged a gift of  million to support the schools new campus project and is a vicechairman of rockefeller university see alsoedit kohlberg kravis roberts list of claremont mckenna college people history of private equity and venture capital private equity leveraged buyout rjr nabisco referencesedit  a b c forbes the worlds billionaires  henry kravis september   jerusalem post the worlds  richest jews    henry kravis september    profile achievementorg accessed september    httpwwwanswerscomtopickohlbergkravisrobertsco answerscom profile  in  kravis was forced to serve as interim ceo of a failing direct mail company advo  refers to henry hillman and the hillman company the hillman company answerscom profile  burrough bryan barbarians at the gate new york harper  row  pp   the biggest deal ever demott deborah a duke law journal  no  lonkevich dan and klump edward kkr texas pacific will acquire txu for  billion bloomberg february    dodson steve beatrice deal is biggest buyout yet the new york times november    fisher lawrence m safeway buyout a success story the new york times october    sorkin andrew ross and rozhon tracie three firms are said to buy toys r us for  billion new york times march    kkr offer of  billion is accepted by first data reuters april    myerson allen r and fabrikant geraldine  buyout firms make deal to acquire regal cinemas new york times january    minchom clive henry kravis  george roberts kkr completes first real estate fund raises  billion jewish business news retrieved  december    henry kravis nndb   harrison s kravis student   nytimescom the new york times  retrieved    hedi kravis chic societys interior designer  new york times april    shaw dan the best revenge isnt it always new york times october    halle johnplaying kraviss tune counterpunch july    thomas landon jr paral